description:
Welcome to Tag Team Tuesdays. This is round 1 of 4 of the live May match up between The Dragons and The Goddesses.
The Dragons are undefeated, The Goddesses have not won a match, and cannot afford to lose another. This is non-scripted Tag Team wrestling at it's best only on Ultimate Surrender, the world's only Non-scripted competitive sex wrestling site!
On paper the teams do not match up, The Dragons have a serious advantage. The Dragon is a stronger, more experienced wrestler than both members of the Goddesses. Holly Heart is bigger and stronger then both opponents, also. There should be no way that the Dragons can lose. However, you cannot measure "heart" on paper and both Isis and Tia know how to dig deep.
